name: PlaneSoundsforSleep
0:

”Alexa ask plane sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: plane sounds
des: The constant hum of an airplane engine is the perfect ambient noise for sleep! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Plane Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
